before we do something new
or difficult or stressful.

13
00:00:27,670 --> 00:00:31,010
It's a phrase we say because
we want people to respond

14
00:00:31,010 --> 00:00:32,409
in a nice, positive way.

15
00:00:32,409 --> 00:00:36,320
So wish me luck, but you
